last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 1
last_episode_to_air.overview: During the French occupation of Syria, Wesh Al-Sa'ad is kidnapped, and her abductor dies before telling  anyone about her identity. She lives in another home, but the person who takes care of her falls in love with her.  In another story, the occupation authorities send the ruthless Colonel Frantz to Syria, to suppress the rebellious movements.
